description: City - East Andover, NHSCHNITZels & GIGGLES is Robert and Alexandra Graf's new adventure. We love the food industry and after 10 years of owning a restaurant & Inn this is the answer. We love to travel so merged the two and VOILA we are on the road selling Chef Bob's amazing food at fairs and festivals all over the East Coast. Be sure to come find us when we are in your area!Come try our delicious German food.
name: Schnitzels & Giggles
